---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const baseUrl = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
const withBase = (path: string): string => `${baseUrl}${path.replace(/^\/+/, '')}`;
---

<BaseLayout
  pageKey="about"
  title="O projektu – BL Prevoz | Javni prevoz Banja Luka"
  description="BL Prevoz je nezavisan projekat za bolju dostupnost informacija o javnom prevozu u Banjoj Luci. Red vožnje, linije, cijene karata i aerodromski transfer na jednom mjestu."
  canonicalUrl="https://blprevoz.com/about/"
>
  <section class="section section--narrow" id="about">
    <div class="container">
      <h1 class="section__title" id="about-title">
        <span data-lang="bhs">O projektu</span>
        <span data-lang="en" style="display:none">About</span>
      </h1>

      <div class="about-content">
        <!-- BHS version -->
        <div data-lang="bhs">
          <h2>Zašto BL Prevoz postoji?</h2>
          <p>
            Javni prevoz u Banjoj Luci obuhvata više prevoznika, a informacije o linijama, redovima vožnje
            i cijenama karata su često raspršene na različitim mjestima ili teško dostupne.
          </p>
          <p>
            BL Prevoz je nastao iz potrebe da se te informacije objedine i učine dostupnim svima —
            jednostavno, pregledno i besplatno. Naš cilj je da ogni korisnik brzo pronađe
            ono što mu treba za kretanje gradom.
          </p>

          <h2>Šta možete uraditi na BL Prevozu?</h2>
          <div class="about-features">
            <a href={withBase('lines/')} class="about-feature">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-route" aria-hidden="true"></i>
              <span>Pregledajte autobuske linije i rute</span>
            </a>
            <a href={withBase('lines/#timetable')} class="about-feature">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-clock" aria-hidden="true"></i>
              <span>Provjerite red vožnje</span>
            </a>
            <a href={withBase('pricing/')} class="about-feature">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-ticket" aria-hidden="true"></i>
              <span>Pogledajte cijene karata</span>
            </a>
            <a href={withBase('airport/')} class="about-feature">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-plane-departure" aria-hidden="true"></i>
              <span>Informacije o aerodromskom transferu</span>
            </a>
            <a href={withBase('updates/')} class="about-feature">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-bell" aria-hidden="true"></i>
              <span>Pratite obavještenja o izmjenama</span>
            </a>
          </div>

          <h2>Nezavisan projekat</h2>
          <p>
            BL Prevoz <strong>nije zvanična stranica</strong> grada Banja Luka, prevoznika niti bilo koje institucije.
            Ovo je nezavisan, volonterski projekat koji nema komercijalnu pozadinu i ne zastupa interese nijednog prevoznika.
          </p>
          <p>Stranica je besplatna za korištenje i razvijena je kao lična inicijativa.</p>

          <h2>Odakle dolaze informacije?</h2>
          <p>
            Sve informacije na platformi prikupljene su iz:
          </p>
          <ul class="about-sources-list">
            <li>javno dostupnih podataka i izvora</li>
            <li>zvaničnih obavještenja prevoznika</li>
            <li>informacija od prevozničkih operatera</li>
          </ul>
          <p>
            Informacije prikazujemo na način koji je koristan za korisnike. Trudimo se da podaci budu tačni,
            ali preporučujemo provjeru kod prevoznika za najažurnije informacije.
          </p>

          <h2>Otvoreni podaci</h2>
          <p>
            BL Prevoz se zalaže za princip otvorenih podataka. Podaci o javnom prevozu su javno dobro i trebalo bi da budu slobodno dostupni svima.
          </p>
          <p>
            Izvorni kod ovog projekta je javno dostupan, a svi podaci prikazani na sajtu mogu se slobodno koristiti.
            Nadamo se da će ovaj pristup inspirisati i druge inicijative za otvorene podatke u našem gradu.
          </p>

          <h2>Budući planovi</h2>
          <p>
            Projekat se aktivno razvija. Neke od planiranih unapređenja:
          </p>
          <ul class="about-sources-list">
            <li>Unapređenje mapa stajališta</li>
            <li>Poboljšanje pretrage linija i ruta</li>
            <li>Proširenje informacija o prevoznim uslugama</li>
          </ul>

          <div class="about-cta">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-comment-dots" aria-hidden="true"></i>
            <div>
              <strong>Primijetili ste grešku ili imate prijedlog?</strong>
              <p>
                Pomozite nam da informacije budu tačnije.
                Ako ste primijetili netačan podatak ili imate ideju za poboljšanje,
                <a href={withBase('contact/')}>javite nam se</a>.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- English version -->
        <div data-lang="en" style="display:none">
          <h2>Why does BL Prevoz exist?</h2>
          <p>
            Public transport in Banja Luka involves multiple operators, and information about lines,
            timetables, and ticket prices is often scattered across different sources or hard to find.
          </p>
          <p>
            BL Prevoz was created out of the need to bring all this information together and make it accessible
            to everyone — simply, clearly, and for free. Our goal is that every user can quickly find
            what they need to get around the city.
          </p>

          <h2>What can you do on BL Prevoz?</h2>
          <div class="about-features">
            <a href={withBase('lines/')} class="about-feature">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-route" aria-hidden="true"></i>
              <span>View bus lines and routes</span>
            </a>
            <a href={withBase('lines/#timetable')} class="about-feature">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-clock" aria-hidden="true"></i>
              <span>Check timetables</span>
            </a>
            <a href={withBase('pricing/')} class="about-feature">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-ticket" aria-hidden="true"></i>
              <span>See ticket pricing</span>
            </a>
            <a href={withBase('airport/')} class="about-feature">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-plane-departure" aria-hidden="true"></i>
              <span>Airport transport information</span>
            </a>
            <a href={withBase('updates/')} class="about-feature">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-bell" aria-hidden="true"></i>
              <span>Follow transport updates</span>
            </a>
          </div>

          <h2>An independent project</h2>
          <p>
            BL Prevoz is <strong>not an official website</strong> of the City of Banja Luka, any transport operator, or any institution.
            This is an independent, volunteer-driven project with no commercial backing and no affiliation with any transport company.
          </p>
          <p>The website is free to use and was developed as a personal initiative.</p>

          <h2>Where does the information come from?</h2>
          <p>
            All information on the platform is gathered from:
          </p>
          <ul class="about-sources-list">
            <li>Publicly available data and sources</li>
            <li>Official operator announcements</li>
            <li>Information from transport operators</li>
          </ul>
          <p>
            We present information in a way that is useful for users. We strive for accuracy,
            but recommend checking with operators for the most up-to-date information.
          </p>

          <h2>Open data</h2>
          <p>
            BL Prevoz is committed to open data principles. Public transport data is a public good and should be freely available to all.
          </p>
          <p>
            The source code of this project is publicly available, and all data displayed on the site can be freely used.
            We hope this approach will inspire other open data initiatives in our city.
          </p>

          <h2>Future plans</h2>
          <p>
            The project is actively evolving. Some planned improvements include:
          </p>
          <ul class="about-sources-list">
            <li>Improving stop maps</li>
            <li>Better search for lines and routes</li>
            <li>Expanding information about transport services</li>
          </ul>

          <div class="about-cta">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-comment-dots" aria-hidden="true"></i>
            <div>
              <strong>Noticed an error or have a suggestion?</strong>
              <p>
                Help us improve the accuracy of information.
                If you've noticed incorrect data or have an idea for improvement,
                <a href={withBase('contact/')}>get in touch</a>.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
